{
  "texts": [
    "In §4.3 we analyze the fine-tuning dynamic and present the training accuracy as function of the fine-tuning duration in Figure 1.",
    "For simplicity we treated the Known categories collectively.",
    "For reference we also include the plot with the full per-category breakdown in Figure 7.",
    "Everything is similar to Figure 3, except that y-axis is the accuracy on the OOD test set.",
    "We note that the development set did not change (not OOD), thus it does not necessarily reflects the optimal stopping point for OOD."
  ]
}